GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 18th March, 2001.
27 Phalguna, 1922(S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 18th March,
2001:-
The Prime Minister relinquished the charge of the office of Minister of
Defence; and
Shri Jaswant Singh assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Defence. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of Minister of
External Affairs.
